Package main.java.models

Class MenuItem

java.lang.Object
main.java.models.MenuItem
public class MenuItem extends Object
The MenuItem class represents a menu item in a restaurant. It is a business object that contains all necessary accessors and mutators for CRUD Operations performed by MenuDAO. MenuItem class is in a 'has-a' relation with MenuDAO (Composition). It contains information such as the name, price, branch, category, availability, and description of each item in the menu

24-Apr-2024
